        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Health Care Workforce Protection from Mandates Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services (CMS) from requiring health care providers to mandate COVID-19 vaccinations for their employees as a condition of Medicare and Medicaid participation, unless the CMS certifies that such a requirement would not result in any staffing shortages.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
